high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the wall, turn right to face the counter and look down at the green bin.
Pick up the apple out of the green bin.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and walk over to the door, turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the apple inside on the middle shelf then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the now chilled apple, then close the fridge again.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the chilled apple inside, then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the microwave.

Pick the apple up from the trash can.
Cross the room and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick up the apple.
Go to the left and face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
